  "detailed_description": "The story of the game is mainly about the magic of Alliria that meets various elves and solves the collapse of the rules that appear in the forest.<br>A relaxed and pleasant story, a simple ARPG, and a brainstorming adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Basic operation</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/f863edb318f8c5eee79099c310b71e61.avif?t=1746943237\" width=475 height=304 /></span><br>You can change the above keys by pressing the  keyboard F1 key.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >system introduction</h2>Magic can be used to attack monsters<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/83f286085eaff379af6347cbe206324f.poster.avif?t=1746943237\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/83f286085eaff379af6347cbe206324f.webm?t=1746943237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/83f286085eaff379af6347cbe206324f.mp4?t=1746943237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In addition to attacks, magical skills can be used to acquire items, assist in customs clearance, and open organs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/056560405da1fdc3d9d44f8a413ca60e.poster.avif?t=1746943237\" width=560 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/056560405da1fdc3d9d44f8a413ca60e.webm?t=1746943237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1047680/extras/056560405da1fdc3d9d44f8a413ca60e.mp4?t=1746943237\" type=\